{"tid":1888571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★第62、25宗確診者在2月6日回港時，二人坐同一架車101X","createTime":"2020-02-20T09:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T09:28:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7efc582c70102d92b7e2b041bf48118a6e315435","tid":1888571,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:28:32.000Z","msg":"澳門追蹤流行病學資料。本港第62、25宗確診者，曾經澳門，昨天澳門說發現這兩宗個案在2月6日回港時，二人坐同一架車101X（10人上車，3人來港，1人已有他電話，另外2人只有名，未聯絡到）、金巴（1700開出，約有30-40人），經港珠澳大橋。呼籲市民如坐過同一班金巴，聯絡當局。當局正追蹤二人搭巴士的情況，但患者未必記得清楚是否坐或站等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/437093/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E5%A2%9E2%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA1%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%9D%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D2%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%9B%BE%E6%90%AD%E9%87%91%E5%B7%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F437093%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E5%25A2%259E2%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA1%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2588%259D%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E5%2589%258D2%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2590%25AD%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B7%25B4&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=2a13fedf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/437093/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E5%A2%9E2%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA1%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%9D%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D2%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%9B%BE%E6%90%AD%E9%87%91%E5%B7%B4</a>"},{"pid":"05994edb84e71355eb4eb745b963932b4ae21193","tid":1888571,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /